{"tid":594803,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎擺低一個起學校 最難忘記嘅柒事","createTime":"2018-03-16T06:42:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-16T06:46:20.000Z","uid":166702,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3d4fe23719e1e4e95b0c0600a182172884a60df3","tid":594803,"uid":166702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T06:42:21.000Z","msg":"我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中學個陣我坐最後 咁我前後左右都係女黎 但坐我隔離個個去到grad都無同佢傾過一句計(學霸黎) 咁一直都相安無事啦<br />\n<br />\n點知有一日食完lunch 點緊名個陣 吾知係咪食完個m記飽得濟 好撚想放屁 係feel到個般屁起個屎忽窿位徘徊 準備一次過爆出梨個隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌 但我真係頂吾撚緊 我已經好努力咁忍住慢慢放 以為無事啦 點知d臭屁臭撚到我自己都聞到作嘔 係似柯爛屎個隻臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 更住眼角見到佢啤撚住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自此我都好乖乖咁聽老師講書 吾傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 直至調左位先正常返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd82f0123215622ae77494d6e03ba424a77082bb","tid":594803,"uid":69083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T06:43:10.000Z","msg":"吾你老母臭柒閪咩"},{"pid":"bff515924ec6d8654f2f8502a3d1b7c356a94ca0","tid":594803,"uid":69083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T06:43:46.000Z","msg":"梨你老母俾車輾開兩截"},{"pid":"ba69d00715cccffaa3abe8079a420fbf631669e0","tid":594803,"uid":137725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T06:46:20.000Z","msg":"同全班講我偶像係笑波子-.- 諗返起真係Ho 7"}]}